  </p>

  <p>
    This work reinforced our belief that healthcare technology must be designed with deep empathy, clinical understanding, and respect for the therapeutic process. The success of this feature has influenced our approach to all mental health products, ensuring that we prioritize human connection and therapeutic outcomes over technological innovation for its own sake.
  </p>

  <p>
    As we continue to evolve our platform, the lessons from Intersession Experiences will guide our development of new features and improvements, ensuring that every addition serves the fundamental goal of improving mental health outcomes through thoughtful, human-centered design.
